klink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_qohor.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Qohor.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 64\">Chapter 64</a>, Daenerys VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403135348\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.025 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.027 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 699/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8872/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3080/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1244/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4880/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   19.185      1 -total\n 74.79%   14.348      9 Template:Ref\n 39.43%    7.565      9 Template:Ref/core\n 20.22%    3.879      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23087-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403135348 and revision id 286856\n -->\n",
